title: Sibinang subung harifwr
lyrics:
Sibinang subung harifwr
Sibinang dhwrwm gurufwr
Sofwinai gaswi alashifwr
Phwrbuni Khamsaliao -2
(a)
Borayw jwng Phwrbuni mungwi
Najaoyw jwng akhai khobjobwi -2
“Sibiyw jwng gonglaiyw jwng
Khulum horw boikhowbw” -2
(b)
Rongza mwnw jwngha Phwrbuniao
Gwjwn mwnw hwngha phwthainayao -2
“Sibiyw jwng gonglaiyw jwng
Khulum horw boikhowbw” -2
